Title: event console: Fix on 'Events of host x' caption and its corresponding link
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: ec
Date: 1694009039
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

Prior to this Werk the hostname, alias and address macros in the hamburger menu of the
Events service were not correctly replaced, causing the 'Events on host x' button and
its corresponding link to be generated incorrectly. This werk fixes that issue.

